<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">candles</ENAMEX>, seem to have been borrowed from <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Hanukkah</ENAMEX>. The center of the <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">eight-day</TIMEX>
