top, and <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">children</ENAMEX> receive <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">Hanukkah gelt</NUMEX> (chocolate coins covered with gold
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">foil</ENAMEX>) and other presents.

